# Synthetic Knowledge Graph based on Noria.ttl schema
# Generated by an AI expert in web semantic technologies and knowledge graphs.

# This file describes a synthetic knowledge graph by instantiating classes and properties
# defined in the Noria ontology. It adheres strictly to RDF, RDFS, OWL vocabularies,
# and TURTLE syntax. All literals are correctly typed and quoted.
# Each entity is linked to at least one other entity via an ObjectProperty,
# and all declared ObjectProperties and DatatypeProperties are utilized.
# The graph aims to be as comprehensive as possible with a maximum number of entities
# and clear descriptions using rdfs:label and rdfs:comment.

# === PREFIXES ================================================================

@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
